    "title": "Circular gattling logic", 
    "comments": [
        {
            "date": "2010-09-28 05:29:00", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "Gattling logic can't loop currently.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }
            ], 
            "name": "secondwtq", 
            "email": "secondwtq"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2010-09-28 05:55:00", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Why should it?\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "renegade", 
            "email": "renegade"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2010-09-29 04:27:00", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "YR's gattling logic can't loop to an artificially specified target.It will re-select target even if the orginal target is ever exist.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }
            ], 
            "name": "secondwtq", 
            "email": "secondwtq"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2010-09-29 07:34:00", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "I'm sorry, I didn't understand that. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Can you rephrase it?\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "renegade", 
            "email": "renegade"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2010-09-30 04:53:00", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Sorry,as a foreigner,I may not express it very nice.\r", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "The orginal gattling logic's \"loop\" is it will retarget after a circle of fire.For AI,it has no problem,but for human players,it will cause large difficulty for operating the unit.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }
            ], 
            "name": "secondwtq", 
            "email": "secondwtq"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2010-09-30 06:55:00", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Though I'm not entirely sure I got what you mean, that sounds more like a bug than a feature to be requested.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "renegade", 
            "email": "renegade"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2010-09-30 10:03:00", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "You know how Yuri's gatling cannon and tank spins faster the longer it shoots at a target?\r", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " I think he means that a gatling weapon always \"resets\" every time it targets another unit and he wants it to continue spinning without \"resetting\" it at all.\r", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " But doing so might break units that have such weapon, unless there's some sort of delay that can be implemented between targeting one to another before resetting.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "drogan", 
            "email": "drogan"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2010-09-30 13:32:00", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "that is fixable using a high RateDown= value. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "RateDown= is the frame delay between going down a step in the gatling weapon's setps. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "In the stock game, this is set to some ridiculously low value like 5 or 10. ", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "Upping this to about 50-70 would be sensible.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "worminator", 
            "email": "worminator"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2010-09-30 14:03:00", 
            "sentences": [
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "I try testing it but it failed.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }
            ], 
            "name": "secondwtq", 
            "email": "secondwtq"
        }, 
        {
            "date": "2010-09-30 15:25:00", 
